></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;Lulu&#039;s ears perk up and she gets an angry look on her face</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&quot;Those two better not be fighting again&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;she storms off to the backyard</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;after she&#039;s gone Ron looks at you</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&quot;Can I ask you something?&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&quot;What?&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&quot;A human raising an anthro, how does that happen? I tried asking Lucille but she won&#039;t tell me anything.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;you sigh</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&quot;It&#039;s a long story, but what the hell?&quot; </div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;you tell him the long, sad story</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;about the man who had given up on his future</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;about the girl who had given up on living</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;how they ended up coming together</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;and how they saved each other</div></li></ol>        </div>
